Q: Using next, modify the code below so that it only prints even numbers.

number = 0

until number == 10
  number += 1
  puts number
end

My A: 

number = 0

until number == 10
  number += 1
  if number.odd?
    puts number.next
  end
end

LS A:

number = 0

until number == 10
  number += 1
  next if number.odd?
  puts number
end